⚡️Types of Acne⚡️

Acne is one of the most common skin conditions, and it affects people of all ages. Symptoms vary depending on the type and severity of Acne. Acne can cause emotional discomfort and scar the skin.

🦠 Main factors that cause Acne:
👉Excess oil (sebum) production
👉Hair follicles clogged by oil and dead skin cells
👉Bacteria
👉Inflammation

Certain things may trigger Acne, such as hormonal changes and specific medications. Factors like diet and stress can worsen it.

The term "Breakout" is very commonly used to describe all forms of Acne. While it might just be a small pimple in the beginning, it could be the starting of an acne breakout. Like any other skin condition, do not ignore and prolong Acne as it can worsen.
